  "purpose": "No-cargo swarm guard for the state where RCH cargo validation is blocked and validation-dependent beads are already waiting. The guard prevents agents from starting new cargo-backed Rust work when the useful next action is either no-cargo evidence or operator-approved RCH unblock work.",
  "inputs": {
